We help companies save 20% to 30% annually by hiring freelancers instead of full-time employees and freelancers increase up to 50% of productive time. Unlike other platforms that take commissions (3% to 40%), Grapevine is commission-free and offers flat-rate, transparent pricing for companies. We also offer specialized tools and resources to automate administrative tasks and manage freelance operations, so companies can focus on growing their business and freelancers can focus on their work. Our goal is to modernize freelance business and establish the largest network of companies and creatives in the arts, design, entertainment, media, and production. We are on a mission to redefine the status quo and create just and ethical work conditions for all. Waveform Technology started in 1992 by installing custom sound reinforcement systems in venues such as schools and churches. By 1994 they moved into the telecommunications industry, where they have remained ever since. Waveform technicians have installed circuits ranging from personal Internet access at home to large fiber optic Metro Ethernet networks. In the late 1990s they helped break the price barrier on T1 circuits, and their dedication to providing affordable and reliable Internet solutions to their customers continues today. In 2012 Waveform Technology successfully launched it's Troy Wireless Broadband product, providing ultra-high-speed broadband Internet and Private Line at speeds up to 500Mb/s inTroy, Michigan. Waveform provides fiber optic based telecommunication and data center services to clients ranging from local governments, non-profits, schools, and companies both large and small. They will work directly with your IT staff to help your company find the solution that is right for your specific requirements.
